WEBVTT

01:51.970 --> 01:57.580
[The Legend of Rosy Clouds]

01:58.670 --> 02:01.940
[Episode 4]

02:22.310 --> 02:23.310
Your Excellency.

02:25.200 --> 02:25.760
Look.

02:28.530 --> 02:31.070
Haven't my painting skills
improved quite a bit?

02:31.070 --> 02:33.000
Even this bird can't bear to leave.

02:33.800 --> 02:35.000
I wouldn't be so sure.

02:37.120 --> 02:38.190
Don't go.

02:43.750 --> 02:45.630
Your Excellency, the bee you drew
on the flower

02:45.630 --> 02:46.960
is truly lifelike.

02:55.470 --> 02:57.030
That's a real bee.

02:57.840 --> 02:58.710
Is that so?

03:02.520 --> 03:04.000
The carrying pole you drew under the tree

03:04.000 --> 03:05.310
looks very realistic.

03:07.390 --> 03:08.520
What carrying pole?

03:08.520 --> 03:09.800
That's a door bolt.

03:11.150 --> 03:12.590
I drew an erhu here.

03:14.790 --> 03:15.390
No.

03:15.420 --> 03:16.880
That's not why we're here.

03:17.150 --> 03:18.150
Your Excellency.

03:22.680 --> 03:23.630
What's wrong?

03:24.870 --> 03:27.150
My two trusted generals,
do you like the iris flowers

03:27.150 --> 03:27.910
I gave you?

03:31.360 --> 03:32.590
If Your Excellency wished to
bestow flowers,

03:32.590 --> 03:33.960
why give us dried ones?

03:34.590 --> 03:36.870
Your Excellency always likes to tease us.

03:36.870 --> 03:39.110
We're here today
to ask Your Excellency about this.

03:39.110 --> 03:40.600
What's wrong with dried flowers?

03:40.600 --> 03:42.520
They're still beautiful
even after being dried.

03:42.520 --> 03:44.520
It'd be a shame not to give them away.

03:48.310 --> 03:49.030
Wei Sui.

03:50.940 --> 03:52.360
I've finished my drawing.

03:52.360 --> 03:53.890
Take it and have it mounted.

04:06.710 --> 04:07.950
Old fox.

04:11.560 --> 04:13.420
The wine last night was poisoned.

04:13.670 --> 04:15.070
-It was poisoned?
-What?

04:15.190 --> 04:17.589
Someone is trying to harm Your Excellency?

04:18.130 --> 04:19.589
The wine was offered to my wife,

04:19.589 --> 04:21.269
but I didn't let her drink it.

04:22.240 --> 04:24.600
But now I'm in the open,
and the enemy is lurking in the dark.

04:24.600 --> 04:26.160
Every move we make from here on

04:26.160 --> 04:27.760
will affect their next move.

04:29.000 --> 04:29.920
So,

04:30.630 --> 04:32.040
we must not alert them.

04:32.720 --> 04:33.920
Then,

04:33.920 --> 04:35.430
what does Your Excellency intend to do?

04:35.430 --> 04:37.560
I need the two of you to help me

04:37.560 --> 04:39.510
root out the treacherous person

04:39.510 --> 04:41.159
targeting Fan Yun, along with the forces

04:41.159 --> 04:42.430
behind them.

04:43.480 --> 04:44.880
Here in the Qi Residence,

04:45.630 --> 04:47.690
there are very few people I can trust.

04:48.120 --> 04:49.380
But these iris flowers

04:50.040 --> 04:51.870
represent my trust in you.

04:52.270 --> 04:54.330
This is also a tradition of my family.

04:55.120 --> 04:57.600
For generations, the rulers of
the Nine Cities have bestowed flowers.

04:57.600 --> 05:00.200
This is the first time
I've ever done so myself.

05:02.390 --> 05:04.450
Wei Ying, Yan Jiang, hear my command.

05:08.920 --> 05:10.180
Yes, Your Excellency.

05:10.280 --> 05:12.030
Though the flowers I bestow this time

05:12.030 --> 05:13.270
are dried,

05:14.120 --> 05:15.970
their significance is immeasurable.

05:15.970 --> 05:17.210
By accepting them,

05:17.680 --> 05:18.750
you pledge

05:19.020 --> 05:21.170
lifelong loyalty to me.

05:22.550 --> 05:23.600
Are you willing?

05:25.040 --> 05:27.360
We're willing to follow Your Excellency
for the rest of our lives,

05:27.360 --> 05:28.600
never wavering.

05:29.160 --> 05:30.310
Good.

05:30.310 --> 05:31.360
Rise.

05:36.070 --> 05:38.480
Ever since Second Young Master Qi
was exiled,

05:38.480 --> 05:41.080
the Nine Cities
have longed for a worthy ruler.

05:42.520 --> 05:44.120
We have waited all this time.

06:01.440 --> 06:02.560
Fan Yun?

06:02.580 --> 06:03.770
Governor.

06:03.800 --> 06:04.670
Perfect timing.

06:04.670 --> 06:06.120
I was just about to look for you.

06:06.120 --> 06:07.160
I have something to discuss with you.

06:07.160 --> 06:08.600
I also have something to discuss with you.

06:08.600 --> 06:10.460
Come on, let's go inside and talk.

06:10.540 --> 06:11.620
There's no time.

06:12.260 --> 06:13.930
Something has come up at my home.

06:13.930 --> 06:15.140
I'd like permission to
leave the residence.

06:15.140 --> 06:16.340
Leave the residence?

06:18.000 --> 06:19.830
Your father holds a post
at the Qilin Pavilion,

06:19.830 --> 06:21.040
and Gao Ran is with the Guardian Corps.

06:21.040 --> 06:22.600
What could possibly be happening
at your home?

06:22.600 --> 06:23.270
Well,

06:23.270 --> 06:24.560
I just received a letter

06:24.560 --> 06:26.390
saying the private school
was bought by someone else.

06:26.390 --> 06:27.850
I want to go back and check.

06:29.030 --> 06:29.910
No.

06:30.400 --> 06:32.260
Right now, no matter what's happening,
you cannot leave.

06:32.260 --> 06:33.190
Go back inside.

06:33.210 --> 06:34.010
Why?

06:34.040 --> 06:34.560
I...

06:39.120 --> 06:41.120
I-I just...

06:41.920 --> 06:42.980
don't feel like it.

06:43.240 --> 06:44.159
I want to paint.

06:44.720 --> 06:47.180
You need to stay by my side
and grind ink for me.

06:47.180 --> 06:48.180
Hurry, go inside.

06:50.070 --> 06:51.330
You don't understand.

06:51.580 --> 06:53.200
I'll station the Guardian Corps
at the gates

06:53.200 --> 06:54.860
so you can't set foot outside!

06:56.020 --> 06:56.780
You...

07:00.390 --> 07:01.520
Where are you going?

07:01.870 --> 07:03.120
Qilin Pavilion!

07:04.480 --> 07:05.800
I'm getting angry now!

07:07.600 --> 07:08.430
Why are you still standing there?

07:08.430 --> 07:09.240
Hurry up and follow her!

07:09.240 --> 07:10.070
Yes.

07:18.460 --> 07:21.100
[Juyun Pavilion]

07:24.920 --> 07:25.630
Boss.

07:26.430 --> 07:27.760
We've found something.

07:28.480 --> 07:29.190
Go ahead.

07:29.750 --> 07:31.960
Fan Yun was originally
the only daughter of the Fan family.

07:31.960 --> 07:33.190
She loved reading

07:33.210 --> 07:35.120
and worked as a teacher
at a private school in Ling'an.

07:35.120 --> 07:35.920
She married

07:35.920 --> 07:37.520
the Governor only recently.

07:39.250 --> 07:40.670
Just an incompetent ruler.

07:40.670 --> 07:41.640
Never mind him.

07:43.600 --> 07:45.210
The walls of the Qi Residence

07:45.680 --> 07:46.880
can't stop anything.

07:47.360 --> 07:48.390
There have indeed been

07:48.390 --> 07:50.680
quite a few scandalous rumors
about Qi Zheng before.

07:50.680 --> 07:52.000
Even after their wedding,

07:52.000 --> 07:54.400
they continued to sleep in separate rooms.

07:54.510 --> 07:58.570
But word has it that they finally
consummated the marriage a few days ago.

07:58.680 --> 07:59.700
So?

07:59.730 --> 08:01.000
So...

08:01.020 --> 08:02.650
I don't really understand these matters

08:02.650 --> 08:03.970
between men and women.

08:03.990 --> 08:06.550
Ling'an is full of beautiful women anyway.

08:06.580 --> 08:08.090
Whatever type of girl you like, Boss,

08:08.090 --> 08:09.970
we'll just find you another.

08:15.070 --> 08:17.270
I just want to hear her play music again.

08:20.950 --> 08:22.120
Do something for me.

08:43.390 --> 08:44.920
Here to admit your mistake?

08:45.720 --> 08:47.600
Wait until I finish
reviewing this memorial.

08:47.600 --> 08:50.260
Then we'll discuss
whether you can leave or not.

08:52.510 --> 08:54.000
What mistake...

08:56.790 --> 08:59.320
does Your Excellency think
I should admit to?

08:59.390 --> 09:00.200
Zheng...

09:00.840 --> 09:02.080
Mr. Zheng.

09:02.080 --> 09:03.840
Who's leaving where?

09:03.840 --> 09:04.630
Me?

09:07.150 --> 09:08.600
I was talking about...

09:11.270 --> 09:12.400
relieving oneself.

09:14.200 --> 09:16.790
Since it's not exactly a refined topic,
I won't elaborate.

09:16.790 --> 09:19.080
Have you come to discuss something urgent?

09:19.080 --> 09:21.120
It's about the matter of raising taxes.

09:21.120 --> 09:22.360
Your Excellency once said

09:22.360 --> 09:24.360
it required further deliberation.

09:24.630 --> 09:25.960
Well, how is that going?

09:26.600 --> 09:27.750
When will it be promulgated,

09:27.750 --> 09:29.550
and when will it be implemented?

09:30.510 --> 09:32.110
I simply found

09:32.110 --> 09:34.480
your arguments
so profound and well-reasoned—

09:34.480 --> 09:36.720
every word a gem, so eloquently put—

09:37.090 --> 09:38.760
that I'm still savoring them.

09:38.910 --> 09:40.910
Savoring them?

09:44.560 --> 09:46.310
The treasury is running dry.

09:46.840 --> 09:48.440
These days, we old officials

09:49.200 --> 09:52.240
can barely get an audience
with Your Excellency.

09:54.640 --> 09:56.680
We understand that Your Excellency

09:56.700 --> 09:58.760
is deeply enamored with Her Ladyship

09:58.770 --> 10:01.140
and has no time for us old folks.

10:01.940 --> 10:03.740
That's only natural, I suppose.

10:05.130 --> 10:06.180
Although

10:06.210 --> 10:08.050
I don't expect

10:08.370 --> 10:09.300
Your Excellency

10:09.540 --> 10:12.020
to be as diligent and devoted as

10:12.420 --> 10:14.350
Second Young Master Qi once was...

10:17.550 --> 10:19.630
I still hope

10:21.600 --> 10:23.440
Your Excellency can

10:23.440 --> 10:25.000
exercise self-discipline

10:25.960 --> 10:27.750
and maintain a proper balance.

10:28.360 --> 10:29.390
Do not...

10:30.480 --> 10:32.390
indulge in sensual pleasures.

10:36.450 --> 10:38.580
I've indeed been neglecting my duties

10:39.240 --> 10:40.670
lately.

10:47.200 --> 10:48.030
Right.

10:49.080 --> 10:50.750
Doesn't the Guardian Corps

10:50.750 --> 10:53.360
hold a martial arts tournament
every two years?

10:53.360 --> 10:54.280
That's right.

10:54.310 --> 10:56.470
It's held to select talents,

10:56.720 --> 11:00.270
and regular competitions
also help improve combat skills.

11:00.790 --> 11:01.550
You... you mean...

11:01.550 --> 11:02.670
That's exactly it.

11:02.960 --> 11:04.750
Could we hold one again soon?

11:04.750 --> 11:06.510
I'd also like to see if the Guardian Corps

11:06.510 --> 11:08.570
has improved over the past two years.

11:09.150 --> 11:10.120
Your Excellency,

11:10.120 --> 11:11.790
the treasury is empty.

11:12.550 --> 11:14.270
We just finished celebrating
Your Excellency's birthday,

11:14.270 --> 11:15.600
and now you want a tournament?

11:15.600 --> 11:18.200
This is hardly the conduct
of a wise ruler.

11:18.200 --> 11:18.840
Well...

11:19.910 --> 11:21.840
We can cover the expenses

11:21.840 --> 11:23.480
by cutting back

11:23.480 --> 11:25.320
on my personal expenditures.

11:26.910 --> 11:28.480
In any case, keep everything
simple and quick.

11:28.480 --> 11:29.680
Hold it immediately.

11:31.790 --> 11:33.050
Yes, Your Excellency.

11:34.670 --> 11:36.670
In the end, he didn't listen to

11:36.670 --> 11:38.500
a word I said.

11:38.530 --> 11:39.490
Mr. Zheng!

11:45.000 --> 11:46.630
Make sure everyone participates.

11:46.630 --> 11:47.390
Remember,

11:47.840 --> 11:49.750
every single person.

11:50.870 --> 11:52.130
Yes, Your Excellency.

12:13.060 --> 12:15.320
Looks like we've had a thief in the house.

12:18.350 --> 12:19.500
Brother.

12:19.520 --> 12:20.780
Don't call me brother.

12:21.510 --> 12:23.200
It makes my skin crawl.

12:23.320 --> 12:24.120
I'm warning you—

12:24.120 --> 12:25.080
if you lay a finger on
my access badge again,

12:25.080 --> 12:26.440
I'll send you straight back to Gao City.

12:26.440 --> 12:27.440
Okay, no problem.

12:27.510 --> 12:29.310
Whatever you say goes, Brother.

12:31.510 --> 12:32.600
I'm going to the Qi Residence today.

12:32.600 --> 12:33.670
The Guardian Corps is holding
a martial arts tournament.

12:33.670 --> 12:34.480
I can't be late.

12:34.480 --> 12:35.460
Have fun by yourself.

12:35.460 --> 12:37.190
Guardian Corps? Qi Residence?

12:37.870 --> 12:38.480
Gao Ran?

12:39.000 --> 12:40.670
Brother! Brother...

12:40.670 --> 12:41.720
Stop right there.

12:41.720 --> 12:42.920
I know what you're trying to do.

12:42.920 --> 12:44.040
No way.

12:45.840 --> 12:47.150
Brother...

12:47.170 --> 12:48.650
I'm so bored

12:48.750 --> 12:50.240
at home every day.

12:50.240 --> 12:51.750
Our parents sent me here
for a marriage alliance,

12:51.750 --> 12:53.870
yet I can't even see the person I love.

12:53.870 --> 12:55.320
I'm so pitiful.

12:55.590 --> 12:56.660
The person you are about to marry

12:56.660 --> 12:58.690
and the one you love are
two different people, right?

12:58.690 --> 12:59.240
Yes.

12:59.270 --> 13:00.440
There is absolutely no way
I'm taking you into the residence.

13:00.440 --> 13:01.120
Give it up.

13:01.120 --> 13:02.200
Why?

13:02.200 --> 13:02.870
Why?

13:03.390 --> 13:04.550
That guy Gao Ran

13:04.550 --> 13:06.030
is as thick as a brick
when it comes to romance.

13:06.030 --> 13:07.000
He's completely clueless.

13:07.000 --> 13:08.840
Why waste your time on him?

13:10.110 --> 13:11.340
Because he's so handsome.

13:11.340 --> 13:12.830
Even if he makes me angry in the future,

13:12.830 --> 13:14.000
at least I'll enjoy looking at him.

13:14.000 --> 13:14.790
Him?

13:15.030 --> 13:15.750
Handsome?

13:15.750 --> 13:16.510
Yes.

13:16.510 --> 13:17.910
Is he as handsome as me?

13:17.910 --> 13:19.230
He is more handsome than you.

13:19.230 --> 13:20.200
You...

13:21.890 --> 13:22.890
See? See?

13:22.910 --> 13:23.690
I can tell from that alone

13:23.690 --> 13:24.910
that your taste is terrible.

13:24.910 --> 13:27.370
You should give up on him
as soon as possible.

13:27.790 --> 13:29.000
Brother,

13:29.000 --> 13:30.330
I was wrong. I was wrong.

13:30.390 --> 13:31.440
You're the most handsome man.

13:31.440 --> 13:32.390
If

13:32.390 --> 13:33.550
Gao Ran is the most handsome in the world,

13:33.550 --> 13:34.840
then you're second.

13:38.080 --> 13:39.000
Get off me. Get off.

13:39.000 --> 13:40.120
No.

13:43.930 --> 13:45.880
Wei Rong, my brother! Do me a favor!

13:45.950 --> 13:46.640
You...

13:50.640 --> 13:53.160
The phoenix soars to the highest heavens,

13:53.180 --> 13:55.090
resting only upon the parasol tree.

13:55.090 --> 13:57.570
A worthy man may dwell in any land

13:57.590 --> 13:59.630
but serves only the master
he deems worthy.

13:59.630 --> 14:00.440
Today,

14:00.440 --> 14:02.720
we convene this martial arts tournament
for two purposes:

14:02.720 --> 14:05.030
first, to gather
heroes and talented warriors

14:05.030 --> 14:06.870
from across the Nine Cities

14:06.870 --> 14:10.400
so that all may showcase their skills
and exchange techniques;

14:10.840 --> 14:11.550
second,

14:11.550 --> 14:12.200
to further...

14:12.200 --> 14:13.110
Slow down.

14:13.150 --> 14:14.240
Block me better.

14:14.240 --> 14:15.950
Select talents,

14:16.320 --> 14:17.720
ensuring that no one

14:17.750 --> 14:18.960
willing to serve the Nine Cities
goes unnoticed.

14:18.960 --> 14:20.120
Where is Gao Ran?

14:20.120 --> 14:21.320
Why don't I see him?

14:21.910 --> 14:22.630
However,

14:22.630 --> 14:24.430
a blade doesn't care who it cuts.

14:24.720 --> 14:25.270
We hope you all

14:25.270 --> 14:27.790
-That one, I think.
-can demonstrate your skills,

14:27.790 --> 14:29.600
-but stop before any real harm is done.
-I see him. There he is.

14:29.600 --> 14:31.390
Good thing I have you,
the Unrivaled Talent of the Nine Cities,

14:31.390 --> 14:32.750
personally appointed by the Governor,

14:32.750 --> 14:34.200
so I can enter the residence at will.

14:34.200 --> 14:36.260
You're truly the pride of our family.

14:36.750 --> 14:38.750
Even though his looks are only average,

14:38.750 --> 14:41.030
everyone has the right to pursue beauty.

14:42.270 --> 14:43.390
Moreover,

14:43.390 --> 14:46.820
it's rare to see you pursue something
with such stubborn determination.

14:46.820 --> 14:48.130
No need to thank me
for such a great favor.

14:48.130 --> 14:49.730
Just remember you owe me one.

14:50.030 --> 14:51.960
You're the one with average looks.

14:54.150 --> 14:55.350
I want some water too.

14:56.100 --> 14:57.300
I'm a little thirsty.

15:00.550 --> 15:02.380
Suyin, pour some tea for His Excellency.

15:02.380 --> 15:03.210
Yes.

15:12.510 --> 15:13.390
This tournament

15:13.390 --> 15:16.840
is being conducted under the principle
of simplicity and efficiency.

15:16.840 --> 15:17.910
The prize is set as follows:

15:17.910 --> 15:20.750
first place will receive 50 taels of gold.

15:22.150 --> 15:23.440
Fifty taels?

15:24.750 --> 15:26.550
You call that keeping it simple?

15:26.550 --> 15:27.920
That's so much money.

15:27.950 --> 15:29.430
I want it too.

15:29.500 --> 15:30.870
It'd be great if I could have it.

15:30.870 --> 15:32.600
Let the tournament begin!

15:48.120 --> 15:49.020
Incompetent.

15:49.390 --> 15:51.080
What a waste of time.

16:03.980 --> 16:04.700
Fan Yun.

16:05.990 --> 16:07.680
Do you want that prize money?

16:08.110 --> 16:09.170
I'll win it for you.

16:10.260 --> 16:10.970
Really?

16:11.000 --> 16:12.050
Of course.

16:13.000 --> 16:13.750
Actually,

16:14.200 --> 16:16.330
I can give you as much money as you want.

16:16.440 --> 16:17.270
Just...

16:18.270 --> 16:20.030
could you stop being mad at me?

16:20.150 --> 16:21.550
Don't ignore me, please?

16:21.900 --> 16:23.470
I wasn't mad.

16:23.960 --> 16:25.480
I was anxious.

16:25.480 --> 16:27.940
I was just worried about
the private school.

16:29.050 --> 16:30.170
Besides,

16:30.230 --> 16:31.760
do I really seem that petty?

16:32.840 --> 16:33.440
Really?

16:34.600 --> 16:35.480
Really.

16:36.510 --> 16:37.840
You're the dignified Governor, after all.

16:37.840 --> 16:38.480
So just

16:38.480 --> 16:40.390
sit here and enjoy the tournament.

16:40.390 --> 16:41.790
How could I just sit here?

16:41.840 --> 16:43.790
I have to win that prize money for you.

16:43.790 --> 16:46.190
Keep the goodies within the family, right?

16:46.870 --> 16:48.030
It won't.

16:48.720 --> 16:49.720
Because...

16:50.510 --> 16:52.770
Because I'm waiting for my Gao Ran to win.

16:53.670 --> 16:54.520
Gao Ran?

16:56.120 --> 16:57.030
Who else

16:57.630 --> 16:59.170
dares challenge me?

16:59.750 --> 17:00.790
Come on!

17:16.920 --> 17:19.050
Move forward a bit. Move forward a bit.

17:28.750 --> 17:30.010
Gao Ran is on the stage.

18:25.270 --> 18:26.480
Since you've won,

18:27.750 --> 18:29.710
why not have a match with me as well?

18:30.780 --> 18:31.710
I wouldn't dare.

18:53.790 --> 18:54.830
A true warrior

18:56.030 --> 18:58.630
doesn't keep retreating
out of mere courtesy.

19:20.060 --> 19:22.140
Now they're both on the stage.

19:22.770 --> 19:24.050
For a moment,

19:24.160 --> 19:26.690
I don't even know
who I should be cheering for.

20:12.730 --> 20:13.790
But no matter what,

20:14.330 --> 20:15.290
those 50 taels

20:15.840 --> 20:17.640
should end up in my hands, right?

20:32.370 --> 20:33.340
Qi Zheng,

20:33.370 --> 20:35.110
in close combat,
your dodges must be quick.

20:35.110 --> 20:36.520
But your attacks must be even quicker.

20:36.520 --> 20:39.070
The moment your sword is
at your opponent's throat,

20:39.070 --> 20:39.880
you win.

20:40.230 --> 20:42.800
If anyone bullies you, Second Brother,

20:42.820 --> 20:44.660
I'll use this move on them.

20:46.110 --> 20:47.240
You're still young.

20:47.240 --> 20:49.300
Focus on protecting yourself first.

20:49.400 --> 20:51.930
Don't keep letting our brothers
push you around.

20:51.930 --> 20:53.440
Come on, one more time.

20:54.510 --> 20:55.350
Once you've mastered it,

20:55.350 --> 20:56.790
I'll take you to see Father.

20:56.790 --> 20:57.750
Okay!

20:57.750 --> 20:59.550
I haven't seen Father in so long.

20:59.750 --> 21:01.280
Thank you, Second Brother.

21:11.200 --> 21:12.160
I lost.

21:24.880 --> 21:25.790
Well done!

21:55.270 --> 21:56.030
Gao Ran!

22:09.350 --> 22:10.160
Gao Ran...

22:13.860 --> 22:14.490
I...

22:15.590 --> 22:17.520
I have something I want to tell you.

22:18.880 --> 22:20.210
I have a second brother.

22:21.700 --> 22:22.900
His name is Qingyuan.

22:26.990 --> 22:28.470
When I was little...

22:30.200 --> 22:31.800
he was the only one by my side.

22:32.910 --> 22:34.170
He was also the only one

22:34.750 --> 22:37.130
who always stood in front of me
and protected me.

22:37.130 --> 22:39.190
When my second brother disappeared,

22:40.350 --> 22:41.510
I cried.

22:42.440 --> 22:44.570
I felt so heartbroken then.

22:46.590 --> 22:48.790
The figure that had always protected me

22:49.070 --> 22:50.790
was gone from my life.

22:51.220 --> 22:52.870
So for all these years,

22:53.680 --> 22:55.530
I've never given up searching for him,

22:55.530 --> 22:57.990
just hoping to see him
with my own eyes again.

22:58.680 --> 23:01.420
Then I could personally return
the position of Governor

23:01.420 --> 23:03.220
that rightfully belongs to him.

23:06.560 --> 23:08.800
But I never could have dreamed

23:10.290 --> 23:11.950
that he'd been here all along,

23:13.110 --> 23:14.310
so close.

23:25.750 --> 23:27.350
I'm not your second brother.

23:28.850 --> 23:30.180
And I don't belong here.

23:32.680 --> 23:35.720
I know there are still many problems
in the Nine Cities.

23:35.720 --> 23:37.830
I know I seem like an incompetent ruler

23:37.830 --> 23:39.430
who neglects state affairs.

23:40.130 --> 23:41.190
But actually, I...

23:42.920 --> 23:44.270
I have my own plan.

23:45.920 --> 23:48.920
I've been waiting for
the right opportunity all this time,

23:48.920 --> 23:50.980
hoping that when he finally returns,

23:52.130 --> 23:54.050
he'll find a better Nine Cities.

24:02.060 --> 24:03.060
I know

24:04.680 --> 24:05.810
your second brother

24:06.010 --> 24:07.680
would definitely be happy to see you

24:07.680 --> 24:08.960
become a true ruler.

24:14.110 --> 24:15.880
But he no longer exists.

24:17.160 --> 24:18.360
Stop looking for him.

24:57.750 --> 24:59.510
You really are good at lying.

25:08.030 --> 25:10.440
If my second brother's spirit
can hear this,

25:10.440 --> 25:11.790
please tell him

25:12.790 --> 25:13.750
that I, Qi Zheng, will definitely become

25:13.750 --> 25:15.110
a worthy governor.

25:18.780 --> 25:21.870
That push-pull tactic might backfire.

25:18.880 --> 25:25.010
[Ningxiang Pavilion]

25:24.400 --> 25:25.110
Look.

25:25.300 --> 25:26.350
Just look at your brother.

25:26.350 --> 25:27.070
-Good tea.
-I don't care.

25:27.070 --> 25:28.070
Another cup.

25:43.490 --> 25:44.240
Stop.

25:53.590 --> 25:54.720
Where are you going?

25:54.920 --> 25:56.510
I need to use the restroom.

25:58.310 --> 25:59.930
Escort Miss Wei to the restroom.

25:59.930 --> 26:01.300
Keep a close eye on her.

26:07.370 --> 26:10.500
She's a grown woman.
Where could she possibly run off to?

26:13.400 --> 26:15.440
Bad news! Miss Wei is gone!

26:18.070 --> 26:18.750
What?

26:22.710 --> 26:23.580
See?

26:23.610 --> 26:25.290
Didn't I say so? Didn't I say so?

26:25.290 --> 26:27.110
The second you take your eyes off her,
she's gone!

26:27.110 --> 26:28.100
What are you yelling for?

26:28.100 --> 26:28.900
I...

26:30.610 --> 26:31.870
I'll help you find her.

26:32.680 --> 26:33.720
Stop right there.

26:34.720 --> 26:35.710
If you go look for her,

26:35.710 --> 26:37.520
I'll have to go look for you later.

26:37.520 --> 26:38.130
I...

26:40.620 --> 26:41.410
Forget it.

26:42.110 --> 26:43.840
I can't keep her under control.

26:44.170 --> 26:46.500
Then let her learn her lesson
the hard way.

26:47.910 --> 26:48.600
Yes.

26:49.400 --> 26:50.560
Let her suffer a bit.

26:53.420 --> 26:54.890
No, seriously, I've noticed...

26:54.890 --> 26:55.850
What?

27:07.440 --> 27:09.300
Governor, have a cup of tea first.

27:13.760 --> 27:14.460
Governor?

27:16.640 --> 27:17.240
Governor!

27:18.560 --> 27:19.520
Have a cup of tea.

27:26.270 --> 27:27.200
Governor,

27:27.640 --> 27:28.930
I've noticed

27:29.200 --> 27:31.460
that ever since you sparred with Gao Ran,

27:31.640 --> 27:32.850
you haven't

27:33.140 --> 27:34.490
quite been yourself.

27:36.880 --> 27:37.640
No. I'm fine.

27:45.000 --> 27:47.260
There's still something I'd like to ask.

27:47.480 --> 27:49.800
You mentioned
Gao Ran used to work as a servant

27:49.800 --> 27:51.260
in your household, right?

27:53.270 --> 27:55.330
Then, when did he come to your family?

27:57.640 --> 27:59.030
About...

28:00.720 --> 28:02.550
13 years ago.

28:03.350 --> 28:05.260
-There was a famine back then.
-Thirteen years ago...

28:05.260 --> 28:06.960
Gao Ran was on the verge of
starving to death,

28:06.960 --> 28:08.480
and my father brought him back.

28:08.480 --> 28:10.080
Did your father ever mention

28:10.160 --> 28:11.440
where he found him?

28:11.440 --> 28:12.830
Did he go into any detail?

28:12.830 --> 28:13.640
No.

28:14.350 --> 28:15.750
We grew up together,

28:15.750 --> 28:17.000
just like family.

28:17.830 --> 28:19.790
So I never asked.

28:20.550 --> 28:21.350
What's wrong?

28:22.340 --> 28:24.820
Why are you suddenly so interested

28:24.850 --> 28:25.960
in Gao Ran?

28:30.860 --> 28:32.460
I'm just a bit envious of you—

28:33.470 --> 28:35.930
having a family member like that
by your side

28:36.830 --> 28:38.230
must make you very happy.

28:40.880 --> 28:43.480
You and Mr. Fan Qi
have treated him well, right?

28:45.880 --> 28:46.790
Of course.

28:47.880 --> 28:49.590
I've treated Gao Ran

28:49.590 --> 28:51.590
like my own brother since childhood.

28:51.590 --> 28:52.440
I even

28:52.860 --> 28:54.490
got angry at Father and him

28:54.590 --> 28:56.850
because Father was always favoring him.

28:58.720 --> 28:59.510
That's good.

29:02.040 --> 29:02.950
That's good.

29:09.750 --> 29:10.830
Are you okay?

29:12.570 --> 29:13.400
Have you...

29:14.430 --> 29:15.400
caught a cold?

29:18.960 --> 29:20.090
I'm not sure either.

29:20.800 --> 29:23.360
I've just been feeling very tired

29:23.380 --> 29:24.530
and weak lately.

29:29.200 --> 29:30.860
You don't have a fever though.

29:31.400 --> 29:32.310
Let me check.

29:46.070 --> 29:47.470
What's wrong, Governor?

29:47.640 --> 29:48.400
Nothing.

29:58.550 --> 30:00.210
Let me have a look around here.

30:20.720 --> 30:21.630
Governor...

30:22.090 --> 30:23.500
what are you doing?

30:25.210 --> 30:27.010
Where did you get this inkstone?

30:27.480 --> 30:28.450
Oh, that?

30:28.790 --> 30:31.720
This was a gift from the students
at the private school.

30:31.720 --> 30:32.590
You like it?

30:34.680 --> 30:35.540
But

30:35.720 --> 30:37.650
I can't give it to you even if you do.

30:39.750 --> 30:41.880
Since it's something you treasure...

30:43.960 --> 30:45.290
I won't take it from you.

30:45.920 --> 30:46.970
If you're not feeling well,

30:46.970 --> 30:48.050
go to bed early.

30:48.680 --> 30:49.810
I'll head out first.

30:56.200 --> 30:57.700
Why did he act so weird?

31:30.360 --> 31:31.620
The water is poisoned.

31:36.760 --> 31:38.220
Your Excellency, well...

31:38.600 --> 31:40.050
Just as I suspected.

31:41.440 --> 31:44.100
This ring changes color
when exposed to poison.

31:44.240 --> 31:46.200
The stain on it came from the ink

31:46.230 --> 31:47.800
on the inkstone in Fan Yun's room.

31:47.800 --> 31:49.640
It seems this matter isn't simple.

31:49.640 --> 31:51.510
They failed to poison her at the banquet,

31:51.510 --> 31:53.970
so they've turned to
the objects around her.

31:54.360 --> 31:56.760
It seems someone
really wants Fan Yun dead.

32:00.480 --> 32:01.740
That woman just now...

32:02.830 --> 32:03.630
Wei Shisan?

32:07.450 --> 32:08.450
That's my sister.

32:11.570 --> 32:12.360
I see.

32:14.110 --> 32:15.770
Let me go see what she's about.

32:15.770 --> 32:16.980
Guardian Corps, listen to my command.

32:16.980 --> 32:19.380
We're now entering the night patrol shift.

32:19.400 --> 32:20.590
Squad on the right,

32:20.770 --> 32:22.640
follow the garden path
through the Qi Residence

32:22.640 --> 32:24.520
and proceed to Ling'an City's main gate.

32:24.520 --> 32:25.840
This squad here,

32:25.860 --> 32:27.510
remain in the garden on standby.

32:27.510 --> 32:29.170
Remember not to let anyone in.

32:29.790 --> 32:30.920
Squad on the left,

32:31.750 --> 32:33.610
head to Ling'an City's east gate.

32:33.680 --> 32:34.680
As for the last squad,

32:34.680 --> 32:36.110
proceed to the west gate.

32:36.110 --> 32:37.350
Is everyone clear?

32:39.830 --> 32:41.030
During the night patrol,

32:41.030 --> 32:42.480
stay alert at all times.

32:44.830 --> 32:46.030
You must be starving.

32:46.110 --> 32:48.570
A feast for the eyes
won't fill your stomach.

32:49.550 --> 32:51.160
You've got a point.

32:51.480 --> 32:52.310
Indeed...

33:28.160 --> 33:29.560
Why are you staring at me?

33:29.880 --> 33:31.070
I'm telling you,

33:31.070 --> 33:32.720
I'm already taken.

33:32.720 --> 33:34.650
Don't get any funny ideas about me.

33:36.440 --> 33:37.730
I do have an idea,

33:38.240 --> 33:39.840
and I want you to do me a favor.

33:43.400 --> 33:44.480
I knew it.

33:45.070 --> 33:47.070
There's no such thing as a free meal.

33:47.200 --> 33:48.440
Go ahead. What is it?

34:01.040 --> 34:02.630
I want you to...

34:08.350 --> 34:10.350
Will you kill me if I refuse?

34:10.370 --> 34:11.480
Of course not.

34:12.000 --> 34:13.000
Then I won't do it.

34:13.030 --> 34:14.489
I'll just make sure you can't get in here

34:14.489 --> 34:16.290
and can't see Gao Ran ever again.

34:37.320 --> 34:38.230
My Lady,

34:38.480 --> 34:39.800
you have a visitor.

34:40.880 --> 34:41.550
Who is it?

34:42.760 --> 34:44.889
It's the eldest miss of the Wei family.

34:48.670 --> 34:49.630
I'm here!

34:50.070 --> 34:51.110
Miss Wei.

34:52.630 --> 34:53.469
You...

34:54.440 --> 34:55.230
Miss Wei,

34:55.670 --> 34:56.630
what

34:57.000 --> 34:58.340
brings you here?

34:58.630 --> 35:00.280
I heard you were sick.

35:03.550 --> 35:04.760
So...

35:04.760 --> 35:06.000
So I'm moving in.

35:09.320 --> 35:10.920
Such impeccable logic.

35:11.520 --> 35:12.510
Did your house collapse?

35:12.510 --> 35:13.840
Could you not curse me like that?

35:13.840 --> 35:14.900
I'm here to save...

35:16.440 --> 35:17.900
I'm here to be your friend.

35:19.110 --> 35:20.800
B-Be my friend?

35:22.000 --> 35:23.440
I have her covered. We don't need you.

35:23.440 --> 35:24.440
You may leave now.

35:30.190 --> 35:30.670
Go.

35:40.960 --> 35:42.070
Fan Yun, sit.

35:43.710 --> 35:44.280
Okay.

36:01.000 --> 36:01.800
You...

36:03.190 --> 36:04.150
Miss Wei,

36:05.030 --> 36:07.550
why do you keep staring at me like that?

36:09.920 --> 36:11.010
When someone's sick,

36:11.010 --> 36:12.530
they need friends around.

36:12.590 --> 36:13.590
And between friends,

36:13.590 --> 36:15.870
we should have a heart-to-heart
and get to know each other.

36:15.870 --> 36:17.380
Get to know each other?

36:19.280 --> 36:20.730
Then, Miss Wei,

36:21.110 --> 36:23.040
how would you like to get to know me?

36:26.230 --> 36:27.880
What's your relationship with Gao Ran?

36:27.880 --> 36:28.840
Why do they say

36:28.840 --> 36:30.800
you're the closest person to him
in the residence?

36:30.800 --> 36:31.630
Gao Ran?

36:32.670 --> 36:33.670
That's because

36:33.670 --> 36:35.800
we've known each other since childhood.

36:35.800 --> 36:36.800
Since childhood?

36:38.650 --> 36:39.400
I'm done for.

36:39.450 --> 36:40.810
What kind of childhood sweethearts story

36:40.810 --> 36:42.010
have I stumbled into?

36:43.760 --> 36:44.840
What do you mean?

36:46.030 --> 36:48.110
Wait, his surname is Gao,
and yours is Fan.

36:48.110 --> 36:50.910
Why have you two known each other
since childhood?

36:51.670 --> 36:53.400
Because when Gao Ran was young,

36:53.400 --> 36:54.670
my father took him in.

36:55.400 --> 36:56.640
But all these years,

36:57.030 --> 36:59.180
I've always treated him
like an older brother.

36:59.180 --> 37:00.930
So if you think about it,

37:00.960 --> 37:02.320
we're basically like siblings.

37:02.320 --> 37:03.880
Siblings?

37:04.620 --> 37:05.800
But you're not related by blood.

37:05.800 --> 37:08.600
What's with all this
"brother" and "sister" talk?

37:08.960 --> 37:10.200
Miss Wei,

37:10.330 --> 37:12.850
didn't you say
you wanted to get to know me?

37:12.960 --> 37:14.960
Why do you keep asking about Gao Ran?

37:15.610 --> 37:16.920
Because I'm not interested in you.

37:16.920 --> 37:18.030
Then you...

37:18.440 --> 37:19.030
You...

37:25.320 --> 37:27.150
I-I get it now.

37:27.150 --> 37:28.800
You like Gao Ran.

37:29.710 --> 37:30.760
Obviously.

37:35.790 --> 37:37.580
So that's it.

37:37.960 --> 37:40.670
So you like Gao Ran.

37:42.400 --> 37:44.150
Even though you're

37:44.570 --> 37:45.850
a bit reckless

37:46.010 --> 37:47.340
and impulsive,

37:48.020 --> 37:50.350
I actually like that about you.

37:54.920 --> 37:56.270
Let me put it this way.

37:56.550 --> 37:59.800
Gao Ran and I have indeed
known each other since childhood,

37:59.800 --> 38:00.840
but I've truly always

38:00.840 --> 38:02.670
regarded him as my own brother.

38:02.670 --> 38:03.230
And he has

38:03.230 --> 38:05.240
always treated me like his own sister.

38:05.240 --> 38:07.040
It's not what you're imagining.

38:09.150 --> 38:10.480
Believe it or not,

38:11.110 --> 38:12.480
that's the truth.

38:13.920 --> 38:15.190
If

38:15.970 --> 38:18.640
you want to be my sister-in-law...

38:21.810 --> 38:22.920
the two of you

38:23.150 --> 38:25.880
do seem like a good match.

38:27.030 --> 38:28.960
Come here, future sister-in-law.

38:29.410 --> 38:30.800
Scoot a little closer. Come on.

38:30.800 --> 38:31.670
Tell me—

38:31.720 --> 38:33.720
just how well-matched are we really,

38:33.720 --> 38:35.120
and in what ways exactly?

38:36.840 --> 38:37.510
Look,

38:37.960 --> 38:39.110
both of you

38:39.570 --> 38:40.860
have a dimple

38:40.890 --> 38:42.370
on the same side.

38:44.400 --> 38:46.120
And you're both

38:46.380 --> 38:48.110
fair-skinned

38:48.110 --> 38:49.320
and adorable.

38:51.880 --> 38:53.080
Very nice. Very nice.

38:53.090 --> 38:54.090
A perfect match.

39:10.630 --> 39:11.360
Tell me more

39:11.360 --> 39:13.820
about your interesting childhood stories.

39:18.150 --> 39:19.510
Miss Wei,

39:20.480 --> 39:22.880
I've been talking
for a whole day and night.

39:23.590 --> 39:25.880
And I've already told you everything,

39:25.880 --> 39:27.510
even what I shouldn't have.

39:28.230 --> 39:30.070
I really have nothing left to tell.

39:30.070 --> 39:31.000
Really?

39:31.620 --> 39:33.020
Then think of more today

39:33.110 --> 39:34.320
and tell me tomorrow.

39:36.150 --> 39:37.950
I have to tell you more tomorrow?

39:38.510 --> 39:39.290
My Lady,

39:39.590 --> 39:41.190
I'm here to attend to you for the night.

39:41.190 --> 39:42.940
-You're here, Suyin.
-I can take care of my friend.

39:42.940 --> 39:43.580
You...

39:43.710 --> 39:44.510
You may leave.

39:53.710 --> 39:55.000
Miss Wei,

39:55.710 --> 39:58.230
I've really told you everything.

39:58.920 --> 40:00.590
What else do you want me to talk about?

40:00.590 --> 40:01.710
Sometimes,

40:02.280 --> 40:04.940
even the people closest to you
can't be trusted.

40:09.920 --> 40:10.840
Nothing.
